            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The standard target assembly consisted of a central",
                "20 mg/cm2 high-purity Al foil guarded on each side by",
                "5 mg/cm2 Al. The guard foils were sufficiently thick",
                "to compensate for 24Na recoil losses from the central",
                "foil. Targets for early experiments contained",
                "polyethylene foils to measure the",
                "27Al(p,3pn)24Na/12C(p,pn)11C ratio"
              ]
            }
          ],
